@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cpgrdm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (tmp + wp.cos(v1))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v0 + 0.77) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.38)))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.19 - (v1 + 0.28 / v1 + 0.51)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v0 + 0.96) - (v2 + 0.40 - v2 + 0.95)))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
